cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this dataset, please cite as below."
title: "doctrine-corpus: A judgment-eliciting Q&A corpus across the shimo4228 research program"
type: dataset
authors:
  - family-names: Shimomoto
    given-names: Tatsuya
    orcid: ""
abstract: >
  A DOI-targeted Q&A dataset that encodes the documented judgment of four
  research lines (Agent Knowledge Cycle, Contemplative Agent, Agent
  Attribution Practice, Authorship Strategy) as bilingual (EN + JA)
  judgment-eliciting Q&A pairs for LLM training. The operational form of
  Authorship Strategy Layer 4 tactic 7 (LLM-first ingest).
keywords:
  - llm-training-data
  - instruction-tuning
  - authorship-strategy
  - agent-knowledge-cycle
  - contemplative-agent
  - doi-registered-dataset
license: CC0-1.0
